===Etymology===
From Greek ''aphorismos'' meaning ''to [[delimit]]'', ''to [[define]]''.
===Noun===
'''aphorism'''
# a short [[phrase]] conveying some [[principal]] or [[concept]] of [[thought]].

===Synonym===
[[maxim]], [[adage]]

